<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٩٢٦ - أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">‌قُتَيْبَةُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">‌سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6932">‌يَحْيَى بْنِ سَعِيدٍ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4100">‌وَعَبْدِ رَبِّهِ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1995">‌وَرُزَيْقٍ صَاحِبِ أَيْلَةَ </a>أَنَّهُمْ سَمِعُوا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4781">‌عَمْرَةَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">‌عَائِشَةَ </a>قَالَتِ: <span class="c2">«الْقَطْعُ فِي رُبُعِ دِينَارٍ فَصَاعِدًا»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>